EN: After the rain, the ground in the courtyard is still a bit shady.

ZH: 在炎热的天气里，喝一杯冰镇饮料更能感到阴凉清爽。
EN: In hot weather, drinking an ice-cold beverage can provide a cool and shady feeling.

ZH: 傍晚时分，夕阳照在山林上，让整个地方都显得阴凉舒适。
EN: In the evening, the setting sun shines on the mountains and makes the whole place feel cool and shady.

ZH: 坐在阴凉的角落里，读一本书十分惬意。
EN: Sitting in a shady corner, reading a book is very pleasant.

ZH: 刚出门的时候，还没有感受到太阳的炎热，只有一丝阴凉。
EN: When just stepping out, there is only a hint of shade without feeling the scorching sun.

